{"tid":1630842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"捉到鬼/藍絲與其鶳不如除哂佢地啲衫褲示眾","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:51:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:07:47.000Z","uid":331341,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"13036d50402575522d2dd23b1e8d3d6eaedece65","tid":1630842,"uid":331341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:51:16.000Z","msg":"下次捉到鬼/藍絲不如剝哂佢哋啲衫褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 將佢咃啲衫褲扔左佢又好燒咗佢又好 唔好比返啲衫佢哋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後將佢咃五花大縛遊街示眾  到時各位手足想 彈佢賓周仔又得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />錫春袋又得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拍片放上YouTube Facebook Pornhub 比大家欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比全世界見到祼體個感覺一定好羞恥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.完全唔需要用任何暴力 但足以羞辱佢哋 和理非一定唔會割 得到更大嘅認同<br />\n2.傷係一時 恥辱係一世  你打鳩佢 好返之後 又一條好漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係比全世界見到祼體嘅羞辱 可能造成一世心理陰影 抬唔起頭做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf968610776a1d4ef57975de42990ddcd725a87b","tid":1630842,"uid":62623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:56:30.000Z","msg":"極重要！唔好俾趁火打劫撚有機可乘！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630661</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dabe603dc2f4c9c81455fc2128157fc5b35cf2a8","tid":1630842,"uid":62623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:56:40.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"2d0404525dcf72f4550bcbcce81db03eea3e63f6","tid":1630842,"uid":329466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:57:30.000Z","msg":"藍屍可以 但唔好又係到捉鬼"},{"pid":"beec69f80e507a803c44e5118695d566b47684a8","tid":1630842,"uid":285997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:57:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" cla